just_use admin_auth.go

# label: CLEAN_INFRA
# role: supports feature — admin session cookies + login page

HMAC-signed session cookies. sessionKey is per-process random, so restarts
invalidate all admin sessions — acceptable given prod restart cadence.
Admin auth is belt-and-suspenders: either a valid gopher_admin cookie OR
Basic-auth on users.is_admin=1 will do. The "API Key" password field on the
form is literally the user's api_key — no separate admin credential store.
